    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >测试你的技能</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Hurling Herman》中深入神秘的地下世界。这款独特的平台游戏挑战您掌握射弹物理学的艺术。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842340/extras/96ed63b589053349be6e0693ca0bfee2.poster.avif?t=1765980105\" width=1000 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842340/extras/96ed63b589053349be6e0693ca0bfee2.webm?t=1765980105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842340/extras/96ed63b589053349be6e0693ca0bfee2.mp4?t=1765980105\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >打造你的道路</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的武器？一个简单的小瓶。你的力量？投掷它并创建临时平台的能力，难以捉摸的阶段块。使用这些方块在险恶的地形中航行，智取致命的生物，并达到令人目眩的高度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842340/extras/462c7ed9f63618ce2e6ec1b570f9b14d.poster.avif?t=1765980105\" width=1000 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842340/extras/462c7ed9f63618ce2e6ec1b570f9b14d.webm?t=1765980105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842340/extras/462c7ed9f63618ce2e6ec1b570f9b14d.mp4?t=1765980105\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >穿越深空的大气之旅</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hurling Herman 共有 40 个关卡，横跨四个不同的地下王国，为您带来一段迷人的旅程。让自己沉浸在游戏大气的配乐中，钢琴和合成器旋律的融合完美地补充了地下环境。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842340/extras/df86bd940606cdfc2340dc6c1ba2f6a0.poster.avif?t=1765980105\" width=1000 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842340/extras/df86bd940606cdfc2340dc6c1ba2f6a0.webm?t=1765980105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842340/extras/df86bd940606cdfc2340dc6c1ba2f6a0.mp4?t=1765980105\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
